\newlabel{tab:cross_seq}{{1}{8}{Pairwise similarity between per-sequence probes at selected layers. Cosine similarity and $\theta _1$ measure directional agreement between probe weight matrices; cross-MSE ratio measures the MSE penalty of applying one sequence's probe to another's activations}{table.1}{}}
