\newlabel{fig:lag_summary}{{4}{9}{Mean lag (token position at which probe $R^2 > 0.9$ minus token position at which model KL converges) by layer. Negative values indicate that the probe threshold is reached before the model's output distribution converges. Error bars show one standard deviation across sequences}{figure.4}{}}
