\newlabel{fig:simplex}{{5}{10}{Belief state geometry at layer 10 as recovered by the encoder-decoder. Each point represents the belief state at one token position, colored by the true hidden state. The distribution follows the expected shape of the Mess3 stationary distribution on the simplex}{figure.5}{}}
